genresAdvancedInfo.name: country boogie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Country boogie is a high-energy style of country music that blends the upbeat rhythms of boogie-woogie piano with the twangy sounds of electric guitars and fiddles. It's perfect for dancing and features catchy lyrics that celebrate good times, partying, and living life to the fullest.
